sequenceDiagram
    participant Main as main.go
    participant G as gossip
    participant ML as memberlist
    participant CW as changeWorker
    participant Pool as connpool.Pool
    participant Consumers as HRW / Syncer / Status

    Main->>G: Start(cfg)
    G->>ML: create memberlist
    G->>ML: join seeds (blocks until first success)
    G-->>Main: ready

    Note over ML,Consumers: Runtime — membership change

    ML->>G: NotifyJoin / Leave / Update
    G->>CW: signal change
    CW->>ML: read current members
    CW->>Main: onChange(snapshot)
    Main->>Pool: evict departed peers
    Consumers->>G: Members()
    G-->>Consumers: current view
